//DO NOT MODIFY SPEED BELOW THIS LINE!! DO NOT MODIFY SPEED BELOW THIS LINE!! DO NOT MODIFY SPEED BELOW THIS LINE!! DO NOT MODIFY SPEED BELOW THIS LINE!!    

    // Collisions
